                                    <h2 class="main-title mb-2">ABOUT <span class="main-title mb-1 brand-color2">N.R.K. PUBLIC SCHOOL</span></h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                    <div class="content-column col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                                        <div class="inner-column">
                                            <p>Welcome to N.R.K. Public School, a beacon of learning established under the Nageshwaram Foundation Trust. Located in Shastri Nagar, Batiya, Jamui, Bihar, our school is dedicated to providing an enriching and comprehensive educational experience for children in our community.</p>
                                            <p>Since our inception, we have committed ourselves to nurturing young minds, fostering a spirit of inquiry, and instilling strong moral values. We believe that every child possesses unique talents and capabilities, and our role is to provide a supportive environment where these can flourish.</p>
                                            <p>Our curriculum is designed to be rigorous yet engaging, balancing academic excellence with opportunities for holistic development through sports, arts, and various co-curricular activities. We strive to create future-ready individuals who are not only academically proficient but also confident, compassionate, and responsible citizens.</p>
                                            <p>At N.R.K. Public School, we are more than just an educational institution; we are a community that values partnership between students, parents, and educators. Together, we work towards shaping bright futures and contributing positively to the progress of our society.</p>
                                        </div>
